---
import PageLayout from '../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import Section from '../../components/sections/Section.astro';
import CTABanner from '../../components/sections/CTABanner.astro';
import Card from '../../components/ui/Card.astro';
import Button from '../../components/ui/Button.astro';
import ScrollReveal from '../../components/animation/ScrollReveal.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Build a Legacy | IBC Academy"
  description="You want to leave more than money ΓÇö you want to leave a system. Discover how the Infinite Banking Concept helps parents create generational wealth that lasts."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <Section background="cream">
    <ScrollReveal direction="up">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <span class="hero-eyebrow">For Parents & Legacy Builders</span>
        <h1 class="hero-title">A Good Man Leaves an Inheritance <br />to His Children's Children.</h1>
        <p class="hero-text">
          Proverbs 13:22 isn't just a verse you highlight in your Bible. It's a mandate. And it raises a question most parents never ask: <strong>What exactly are you leaving?</strong>
        </p>
        <p class="hero-text">
          A pile of money gets spent in a generation. A house gets sold. A brokerage account gets divided, taxed, and depleted. But a <em>system</em> ΓÇö a way of thinking about money that your children can use, teach, and pass on ΓÇö that's a legacy.
        </p>
        <p class="hero-text">
          This 6-article journey will show you what generational wealth actually looks like, why most families lose it, and how one concept ΓÇö the Infinite Banking Concept ΓÇö gives you a framework to build something that outlasts you.
        </p>
      </div>
    </ScrollReveal>
  </Section>

  <!-- What This Is (And Isn't) -->
  <Section title="What This Journey Is (And Isn't)">
    <ScrollReveal direction="up">
      <div class="clarity-content">
        <div class="clarity-grid">
          <div class="clarity-box">
            <h3 class="clarity-heading is-not">This is NOT:</h3>
            <ul class="clarity-list">
              <li>A way to get rich so your kids don't have to work</li>
              <li>A trust-fund strategy for the already wealthy</li>
              <li>A complicated estate planning pitch</li>
              <li>Something that requires a huge income</li>
              <li>A replacement for teaching your kids character</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="clarity-box">
            <h3 class="clarity-heading is-yes">This IS:</h3>
            <ul class="clarity-list">
              <li>A system any family can start ΓÇö at any income</li>
              <li>A way to fund college, cars, and life on your terms</li>
              <li>A financial education you can hand to your kids</li>
              <li>A multi-generational wealth transfer strategy</li>
              <li>A biblical principle put into practice</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="clarity-footer">
          By the end, you'll understand how ordinary families build extraordinary legacies ΓÇö not through luck or high income, but through a system that compounds across generations.
        </p>
      </div>
    </ScrollReveal>
  </Section>

  <!-- The 6 Articles -->
  <Section title="Your 6-Article Journey" subtitle="Each article takes about 8-10 minutes to read. Written for parents who want to do more than hope their kids will be okay." background="cream">
    <div class="journey-grid">
      <ScrollReveal direction="up" delay={0}>
        <a href="/learn/articles/parent-01-what-legacy-means" class="journey-card-link">
          <div class="journey-card">
            <span class="journey-number">01</span>
            <h3 class="journey-title">What "Leaving a Legacy" Actually Means</h3>
            <p class="journey-desc">It's not just money. It's not just values. It's a system that teaches both ΓÇö and survives you.</p>
          </div>
        </a>
      </ScrollReveal>
      <ScrollReveal direction="up" delay={100}>
        <a href="/learn/articles/parent-02-family-banking-system" class="journey-card-link">
          <div class="journey-card">
            <span class="journey-number">02</span>
            <h3 class="journey-title">The Family Banking System</h3>
            <p class="journey-desc">How one policy becomes a multi-generational engine ΓÇö and why families who bank privately build wealth differently.</p>
          </div>
        </a>
      </ScrollReveal>
      <ScrollReveal direction="up" delay={200}>
        <a href="/learn/articles/parent-03-teaching-kids-money" class="journey-card-link">
          <div class="journey-card">
            <span class="journey-number">03</span>
            <h3 class="journey-title">Teaching Your Kids About Money</h3>
            <p class="journey-desc">Stop lecturing. Start showing. The most powerful financial education happens when your kids watch you use the system.</p>
          </div>
        </a>
      </ScrollReveal>
      <ScrollReveal direction="up" delay={300}>
        <a href="/learn/articles/parent-04-college-funding-myth" class="journey-card-link">
          <div class="journey-card">
            <span class="journey-number">04</span>
            <h3 class="journey-title">The College Funding Trap</h3>
            <p class="journey-desc">529s, student loans, and the assumption that college costs have to break you. There's a better way ΓÇö and it doesn't lock your money up.</p>
          </div>
        </a>
      </ScrollReveal>
      <ScrollReveal direction="up" delay={400}>
        <a href="/learn/articles/parent-05-generational-transfer" class="journey-card-link">
          <div class="journey-card">
            <span class="journey-number">05</span>
            <h3 class="journey-title">How Wealth Actually Transfers</h3>
            <p class="journey-desc">70% of families lose their wealth by the second generation. 90% by the third. Here's why ΓÇö and how to be the exception.</p>
          </div>
        </a>
      </ScrollReveal>
      <ScrollReveal direction="up" delay={500}>
        <a href="/learn/articles/parent-06-proverbs-1322" class="journey-card-link">
          <div class="journey-card">
            <span class="journey-number">06</span>
            <h3 class="journey-title">Proverbs 13:22 in Practice</h3>
            <p class="journey-desc">A good man leaves an inheritance to his children's children. Here's what that looks like with actual numbers and a real system.</p>
          </div>
        </a>
      </ScrollReveal>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <!-- Why This Matters -->
  <Section title="Why Bother?">
    <ScrollReveal direction="up">
      <div class="why-content">
        <p class="why-text">
          Here's the question that keeps parents up at night:
        </p>
        <blockquote class="why-quote">
          "What happens to my family when I'm gone?"
        </blockquote>
        <p class="why-attribution">ΓÇö The question every parent eventually asks</p>
        <p class="why-text">
          Most people answer it with life insurance, a will, maybe a 529 plan. But those are products, not systems. Products get consumed. Systems keep producing.
        </p>
        <p class="why-text">
          Nelson Nash, a forester and the creator of the Infinite Banking Concept, spent decades studying how money works across generations. His conclusion: the families that build lasting wealth don't just save money ΓÇö they <em>control the banking function</em> in their lives.
        </p>
        <p class="why-text">
          When you become your own banker, you don't just leave your kids money. You leave them a process. A way of thinking. A family bank that can fund their education, their first home, their business ΓÇö and their children's future after that.
        </p>
        <p class="why-text">
          That's not a financial plan. That's a legacy.
        </p>
      </div>
    </ScrollReveal>
  </Section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <Section background="cream">
    <ScrollReveal direction="up">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h2 class="cta-title">Ready to Start?</h2>
        <p class="cta-text">
          Article 1 redefines what legacy actually means. It takes about 8 minutes. No signup. No pitch. Just a different way of thinking about what you're building for your family.
        </p>
        <div class="cta-button">
          <Button variant="primary" size="lg" href="/learn/articles/parent-01-what-legacy-means">
            Begin Article 1 ΓåÆ
          </Button>
        </div>
        <p class="cta-note">
          Not ready yet? Bookmark this page. Your family's future isn't going anywhere ΓÇö but neither is this information.
        </p>
      </div>
    </ScrollReveal>
  </Section>

  <!-- Final Note -->
  <CTABanner
    heading="Have Questions?"
    description="Join our free community where 500+ people are learning together. Ask anything. No pressure."
    buttonText="Join the Conversation"
    buttonHref="https://skool.com/ibc-academy"
  />
</PageLayout>

<style>
  /* Hero Section */
  .hero-content {
